# Sponza glTF source (downloaded separately by sandbox build).
# Khronos's Sample-Assets Sponza .gltf + .bin total ~10 MB; the
# referenced .jpg textures (which we don't ship since materials
# aren't wired yet) would add ~50 MB. The bake produces only the
# .kscene + .kmesh files which live under build/, also ignored.
assets/source/scenes/Sponza/
